{{Infobox serial killer | name=Filiberto Hernández Martínez | image= | caption= | birthname= | alias=''"The Tamuin Monster"'', ''"the Beast Tamuin"'' or ''"the Tamuin Strangler"'' | birth_date=1971 | birth_place=[[Ebano, San Luis Potosi|Ebano]], [[San Luis Potosi]], [[Mexico]] | death_date= | cause= | victims= 6 | country=[[Mexico]] | states=[[San Luis Potosi]] | beginyear=2010 | endyear=2014 | apprehended=July 5, 2014 | penalty= [[Life imprisonment]] }}
'''Filiberto Hernández Martínez''' (born 1971) was a [[Mexicans|Mexican]] [[serial killer]] active between 2010 and 2013.<ref>{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=Filiberto Hernandez, Child Serial Killer Suspect, Confesses To 5 Murders: Cops |url=http://www.omahasuntimes.com/2014/07/filiberto-hernandez-child-serial-killer-suspect-confesses-to-5-murders-cops/ |newspaper=Omaha Sun Times |location=Omaha, Nebraska, USA |date=5 July 2014 |accessdate=17 January 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402191055/http://www.omahasuntimes.com/2014/07/filiberto-hernandez-child-serial-killer-suspect-confesses-to-5-murders-cops/ |archive-date=2 April 2015 |url-status=dead }}</ref> His crimes took place in [[Tamuín]], in southern of [[San Luis Potosi]] state, allegedly murdered four children and a woman,<ref>{{cite news |last1=Rama |first1=Anahi |last2=Diaz |first2=Lizbeth |last3=Murray |first3=Christine |date=8 July 2014 |title=Mexico police detain alleged serial child killer |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/08/us-mexico-murder-idUSKBN0FB03X20140708 |newspaper=Thomson Reuters |location=USA |accessdate=17 January 2015 |quote=Mexican police have detained a man who allegedly murdered four children and a woman in a small town in the center of the country, authorites &#91;sic&#93; said on Saturday, as statistics show a marked increased in the number of women being murdered... }}</ref> before other [[feminicide]] was attributed him.<ref>{{cite news |last=González Vázquez |first=Antonio |date=30 July 2014 |title=Nueva orden de aprehensión contra homicida de SLP |trans-title=New apprehension order for killer of San Luis Potosi |url=http://www.milenio.com/estados/homicida_de_SLP-homicida_confeso-homicida_de_ninas_0_344965718.html |language=Spanish |newspaper=Milenio Diario |location=San Luis Potosi, Mexico |accessdate=17 January 2015 }}</ref>
==Biography== In 1971, Filiberto Hernández born in Ebano, San Luis Potosi; within an impoverished family. He had 3 brothers and 2 sisters. According to his father, Marcelino Hernández, he was a normal boy, had worked from a young age, and only studied to a high school level, and enlisted in the military when he was 17 years old.<ref>{{cite news |last=Galicia |first=Myrtha |date=10 July 2014 |title=Filiberto buscó su propia desdicha |trans-title="Filiberto searched his own unhappiness" |url=http://pulsoslp.com.mx/2014/07/10/filiberto-busco-su-propia-desdicha/ |language=Spanish |newspaper=Pulso |location=San Luis Potosi, Mexico |accessdate=17 January 2015 }}</ref>
